title: [The Coventry, Tree Top]
description: Cerulean silk drapes in wide swathes from the latticework ceiling above, and tiny motes of light dart in and out of the leaves of the limbs incorporated into the oaken walls enclosing this space.  Irreglarly cut shelves of marled oak are perched atop branches here and there to serve as displays, while a pair of woven grapevine baskets dangle from natural fiber cording fixed to the supports above.
